For this task, I used Google Forms and Google Sheets as the primary platforms. I created a Digital Literacy Awareness Quiz with five questions, including multiple-choice, short answer, and other formats to test my batchmates understanding of online safety, privacy, and digital skills. Google Forms allowed me to design the quiz quickly and share it through a simple link, while Google Sheets automatically collected and organized responses for easy analysis.
